Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是納豆上有的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\an8\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&\fad(0,100)}s.cerevisiae 絮凝酵母\N全名Saccharomyces cerevisiae
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麵包店裡有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部給我回答上來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當真嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙也嚇到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要說你連細菌的心情都懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…嗯…怎麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 今天到此為止吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對無法認可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說全世界的細菌你都能看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類用了長久的時間一點一點發現的菌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如此輕易就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被知識都不如我的這種小屁孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來她相當受打擊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 因為太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自知很失禮 但可以說一句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 你是bondage癖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs27\fad(0,100)}bondage：束縛身體的一種龐克服裝 多為皮革或閃亮的材質  也是SM界的用語
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\pos(762,414)\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&\fad(0,100)}T.rubrum 紅色毛癬菌\N即腳氣菌\N全名Trichophyton rubrum
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡建大家的家園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要做自己的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長谷川小姊 還沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的是乾燥清潔 以及醫師正確的處理
