Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 螢 這房間裡有hiyoti
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 如果把hiyoti那種東西帶回老家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白從哪裡飄來的嗎 澤木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:18:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡 螢
